"Then you can browse these URLs by clicking on them with @kbd{Mouse-2} (or "
"@kbd{Mouse-1} quickly) or by moving to one and typing @kbd{C-c @key{RET}}.  "
"@xref{Goto Address mode, Activating URLs, Activating URLs}."
